ained using the second drift closure (referred to as DF2).\nFurther, in conformity with the DNS, theory shows that the clustering of\n$St_\\eta \\ll 1$ particles is only weakly anisotropic.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Aug 2018 18:58:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-26"}
