ariance in ADI detection limits and 30%-50% of the variance in\nRDI detection limits. Averaged over a range of angular separations, our models\npredict both ADI and RDI contrast to within a factor of 2. These results\nilluminate important factors in high-contrast imaging observations with the\nNIRC2 vortex coronagraph, help improve observing strategies, and inform future\nupgrades to the hardware.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Aug 2018 22:25:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-26"}
